<bibRefCitation id="EFCA32FEA524FF836A69BF81CB8CFE43" author="de Meijere JCH" box="[279,478,468,490]" pageId="49" pageNumber="148" pagination="191 - 332" refId="ref55623" refString="de Meijere JCH. 1908. Studien uber sudostasiatische Dipteren. III. Tijdschrift Voor Entomologie 51: 191 - 332. pls. 7 - 8." type="journal article" year="1908">de Meijere (1908)</bibRefCitation>
cited the type material as follows: ‘Neu-Guinea: Moroka, 
<specimenCount id="9D5D8486A524FF836973BFA6C86DFDA1" box="[525,575,499,520]" pageId="49" pageNumber="148" type="male">1 ♂</specimenCount>
, Loria leg. (Mus. Genua)’. 
